This Sunday will see the last Premier League fixtures for 2019. Arsenal welcome Chelsea in a keenly anticipated clash, with Mikel Arteta set to take charge of his first home game. Liverpool take on Wolverhampton Wanderers at Anfield. The last fixture is between Manchester City and Sheffield United at the Etihad. Sunday, December 29
15:00 Arsenal vs Chelsea
17:30 Liverpool vs Wolverhampton Wanderers
